PPC Says Sales in South Africa’s Cement Industry in 2011 May Mirror 2010’s

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-05-17T05:14:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/ppc-says-sales-in-south-africa-s-cement-industry-in-2011-may-mirror-2010-s.html
Pretoria Portland Cement Co. says
sales by the South African cement industry may be similar in
2011 to 2010.  While the rate of decline in demand is slowing the company
expects the year to be “challenging.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  